dashboard.description: A dynamic list of non-voting jobs per branch

targets.query: SELECT count("result_num"), mean("duration"), max("duration"), mean("container_prep_time_u"), max("container_prep_time_u"), sum("duration"), sum("result_num")*100/count("result_num")  FROM "autogen"."build" WHERE ("type" = 'upstream' AND "job_name" =~ /.*tripleo-.*/ AND "voting" = 'False' AND "branch" = 'master' ) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "project"
